HEADWORD: Gradually
<hw>Grad"u*al*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>In
a gradual manner.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>In degree.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
