<p><q>Human reason doth not only <qex>gradually</qex>, but specifically,
differ from the fantastic reason of brutes.</q>
<rj><qau>Grew.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gradualness</ent>⟦br⟧
